cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep neural network for semantic segmentation of cellular structures in electron tomography images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The network architecture is fully convolutional and end-to-end, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of multi-scale and multi-level contextual information, which suggests a potential focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
